---
// Article 3.1: LHDN and e-Filing
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../../components/Footer.astro';
import AudienceTabs from '../../../components/AudienceTabs.astro';
import Breadcrumb from '../../../components/panduan-rakyat/Breadcrumb';

const articleData = {
  sectionNumber: '03',
  sectionTitle: 'Tax and Finance',
  sectionIcon: '💰',
  articleTitle: 'LHDN and e-Filing',
  articleDescription: 'How to register, file taxes, and manage your tax account',
  colorRgb: '5, 150, 105',
  lastUpdated: 'March 2026',
};

const simpleContent = `
  <h2 id="what-is-lhdn">What is LHDN?</h2>
  <p>LHDN (Lembaga Hasil Dalam Negeri) is the Inland Revenue Board of Malaysia. They collect income tax from individuals and businesses.</p>
  
  <h2 id="who-must-file">Who must file taxes?</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>✅ Malaysians earning above RM34,000/year (after EPF)</li>
    <li>✅ Foreigners working in Malaysia</li>
    <li>✅ Business owners and freelancers</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="how-to-register">How to register:</h2>
  <ol>
    <li><strong>Get file number:</strong> Visit LHDN office or call 03-8911 1000</li>
    <li><strong>Register online:</strong> Go to hasil.gov.my</li>
    <li><strong>Activate e-Filing:</strong> Request activation code</li>
    <li><strong>File taxes:</strong> Submit before April 30 every year</li>
  </ol>

  <h2 id="important-dates">Important dates:</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>e-Filing deadline:</strong> April 30 (individuals)</li>
    <li><strong>Manual filing:</strong> April 30</li>
    <li><strong>Business tax:</strong> Within 7 months of financial year-end</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="important-numbers">Important numbers:</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>LHDN Hotline:</strong> 03-8911 1000</li>
    <li><strong>Website:</strong> hasil.gov.my</li>
  </ul>
`;

const detailedContent = `
  <h2 id="overview">Overview</h2>
  <p>The Lembaga Hasil Dalam Negeri (LHDN) or Inland Revenue Board of Malaysia administers the self-assessment tax system. All eligible individuals must file annual tax returns.</p>

  <h2 id="who-must-file">Who Must File Tax Returns?</h2>
  <h3>Individuals:</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>✅ Employed individuals with annual income > RM34,000 (after EPF)</li>
    <li>✅ Self-employed/freelancers with any income</li>
    <li>✅ Business owners</li>
    <li>✅ Foreigners working in Malaysia (any income)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="registration">How to Register for Tax File Number</h2>
  <h3>Option 1: Visit LHDN Office</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Bring IC/passport and proof of income (employment letter, payslips)</li>
    <li>Fill out registration form</li>
    <li>Receive tax file number immediately</li>
  </ol>

  <h3>Option 2: Online Registration</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Visit <strong>hasil.gov.my</strong></li>
    <li>Click "e-Daftar" for new registration</li>
    <li>Fill in personal and income details</li>
    <li>Receive file number via email</li>
  </ol>

  <h2 id="efiling">How to Use e-Filing</h2>
  <h3>Step 1: Activate e-Filing</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Go to <strong>hasil.gov.my</strong></li>
    <li>Click "e-Filing" → "Request Activation Code"</li>
    <li>Enter tax file number and IC</li>
    <li>Activation code sent via post (takes 7-10 days)</li>
  </ol>

  <h3>Step 2: File Your Taxes</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Login to e-Filing with file number and password</li>
    <li>Select Form B (business income) or Form BE (employment income)</li>
    <li>Enter income details from EA form (given by employer)</li>
    <li>Claim tax reliefs and deductions</li>
    <li>Review and submit</li>
    <li>Pay any additional tax (if applicable)</li>
  </ol>

  <h2 id="tax-forms">Tax Forms</h2>
  <table class="w-full border-collapse border border-border my-4">
    <thead><tr class="bg-muted"><th class="border border-border p-3 text-left">Form</th><th class="border border-border p-3 text-left">For Whom</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td class="border border-border p-3">Form BE</td><td class="border border-border p-3">Employment income only</td></tr>
      <tr><td class="border border-border p-3">Form B</td><td class="border border-border p-3">Business income + employment</td></tr>
      <tr><td class="border border-border p-3">Form M</td><td class="border border-border p-3">Non-residents</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2 id="important-dates">Important Dates</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Individual e-Filing:</strong> April 30</li>
    <li><strong>Manual filing:</strong> April 30</li>
    <li><strong>Company tax (Form C):</strong> Within 7 months of financial year-end</li>
    <li><strong>PCB (monthly tax):</strong> By 15th of following month</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="payment-methods">Tax Payment Methods</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>✅ Online banking (Maybank2u, CIMB Clicks, etc.)</li>
    <li>✅ Credit/debit card</li>
    <li>✅ LHDN counter</li>
    <li>✅ Post office</li>
    <li>✅ FPX (Financial Process Exchange)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="important-numbers">Important Contacts</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Hotline:</strong> 03-8911 1000</li>
    <li><strong>Website:</strong> hasil.gov.my</li>
    <li><strong>Email:</strong> callcentre@hasil.gov.my</li>
    <li><strong>Live Chat:</strong> Available on website (Mon-Fri, 8 AM-5 PM)</li>
  </ul>
`;

const faqs = [
  {
    question: "What if I miss the filing deadline?",
    answer: "You'll face penalties: 10% fine on tax owed + possible legal action. File immediately even if late. LHDN may waive penalties for first-time offenders with reasonable excuse."
  },
  {
    question: "Do I need to file if tax is fully deducted (PCB)?",
    answer: "Yes, you must still file even if PCB covers your full tax. Filing is mandatory if income exceeds RM34,000/year (after EPF), regardless of PCB status."
  },
  {
    question: "What documents do I need for e-Filing?",
    answer: "EA Form (from employer), receipts for tax reliefs (medical, education, insurance), donation receipts, and EPF contribution statement."
  },
  {
    question: "Can I file taxes myself or do I need an agent?",
    answer: "Most individuals can file themselves using e-Filing. Consider a tax agent only if you have complex situations (multiple income sources, foreign income, business losses)."
  },
  {
    question: "What happens if I overpay tax?",
    answer: "LHDN will refund the excess amount via bank transfer. Ensure your bank details are updated in e-Filing. Refunds typically take 14-30 days."
  }
];

const headings = [
  { id: 'overview', title: 'Overview', level: 2 },
  { id: 'who-must-file', title: 'Who Must File?', level: 2 },
  { id: 'registration', title: 'How to Register', level: 2 },
  { id: 'efiling', title: 'How to Use e-Filing', level: 2 },
  { id: 'tax-forms', title: 'Tax Forms', level: 2 },
  { id: 'important-dates', title: 'Important Dates', level: 2 },
  { id: 'payment-methods', title: 'Payment Methods', level: 2 },
];
---

<Layout title={`${articleData.articleTitle} | People's Guide | EduLaluan`}>
  <Header />
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-background">
    <section class="relative overflow-hidden py-section-lg border-b" style={{'--section-color': `rgb(${articleData.colorRgb})`,'border-bottom-color': `rgb(${articleData.colorRgb})`}}>
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="max-w-4xl">
          <Breadcrumb items={[{label:'Home',href:'/'},{label:"People's Guide",href:'/panduan-rakyat'},{label:`Section ${articleData.sectionNumber}`,href:`/panduan-rakyat/section-${articleData.sectionNumber}`},{label:articleData.articleTitle}]} />
          <a href={`/panduan-rakyat/section-${articleData.sectionNumber}`} class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-primary transition-colors mb-6"><svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7" /></svg>Back to Section {parseInt(articleData.sectionNumber).toString()}</a>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mt-6"><div class="flex h-16 w-16 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-xl text-3xl" style={{'backgroundColor': `rgb(${articleData.colorRgb})`,'color': 'white'}}>{articleData.sectionIcon}</div><div class="flex-1"><p class="text-sm font-medium text-primary mb-1 tracking-wide uppercase">Section {parseInt(articleData.sectionNumber).toString()}: {articleData.sectionTitle}</p><h1 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-foreground">{articleData.articleTitle}</h1><p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground mt-3">{articleData.articleDescription}</p></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="py-section-md bg-surface">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="flex gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
            <AudienceTabs>
              <Fragment slot="simple" set:html={simpleContent} />
              <Fragment slot="detailed" set:html={detailedContent} />
            </AudienceTabs>
            <div class="mt-12"><h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-6">Frequently Asked Questions</h2><div class="space-y-3">{faqs.map((faq)=>(<details class="group rounded-xl border bg-surface-elevated transition-all"><summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 font-semibold text-foreground list-none">{faq.question}<svg class="h-5 w-5 text-muted-foreground transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" /></svg></summary><div class="px-5 pb-5 text-muted-foreground">{faq.answer}</div></details>))}</div></div>
            <div class="mt-12 pt-6 border-t border-border"><p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground"><strong>Last updated:</strong> {articleData.lastUpdated}</p></div>
          </div>
          <aside class="sticky top-24 hidden lg:block w-64 shrink-0"><nav class="space-y-1" aria-label="Table of contents"><h3 class="text-xs font-semibold text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">On This Page</h3>{headings.map((heading)=>(<a href={`#${heading.id}`} class="block py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground transition-colors" style={{paddingLeft:`${(heading.level-2)*12+12}px`}}>{heading.title}</a>))}</nav></aside>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="py-section-md bg-background"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl"><div class="rounded-2xl border bg-surface-elevated p-6"><div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-muted-foreground"><svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg><p class="text-sm"><strong>Disclaimer:</strong> This guide provides general information only. Always verify with official sources for the most current information.</p></div></div></div></div></section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
<style>:root{--section-padding-lg:clamp(3rem,5vw + 1rem,5rem);--section-padding-md:clamp(2rem,3vw + 1rem,3rem)}.py-section-lg{padding-top:var(--section-padding-lg);padding-bottom:var(--section-padding-lg)}.py-section-md{padding-top:var(--section-padding-md);padding-bottom:var(--section-padding-md)}.prose-panduan{font-size:var(--text-base);line-height:var(--leading-relaxed);color:var(--foreground)}.prose-panduan h2{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:var(--text-2xl);font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem;color:var(--foreground)}.prose-panduan h3{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:var(--text-xl);font-weight:600;margin-top:2rem;margin-bottom:0.75rem;color:var(--foreground)}.prose-panduan p{margin-bottom:1.25rem}.prose-panduan ul,.prose-panduan ol{margin-bottom:1.25rem;padding-left:1.5rem}.prose-panduan li{margin-bottom:0.5rem}.prose-panduan a{color:var(--primary);text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:2px}.prose-panduan a:hover{color:var(--primary-dark)}.prose-panduan strong{font-weight:600;color:var(--foreground)}.prose-panduan table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:1.5rem 0}.prose-panduan th{background-color:var(--muted);font-weight:600;padding:0.75rem;border:1px solid var(--border)}.prose-panduan td{padding:0.75rem;border:1px solid var(--border)}.prose-panduan .bg-muted{background-color:var(--muted);padding:1rem;border-radius:0.5rem;margin:1.5rem 0}</style>
